My concept was that the battle of Sekigahara happened
on October 21st, 1600 and not September 15th, 1600,
other events happened, like the Dutch ship sailing
into Japanese land.

--- "Anthony J. Bryant" <ajbryant@...> wrote:
> deondejonghsa wrote:
> 
> > I get conflicting dates as to when this happened.
> > Was it on October 21st, 1600 or September 15 1600?
> 
> Both.
> 
> It was on the 15th day of the Ninth Lunar Month, a
> date which, in 1600, corresponded to
> Oct. 21.
> 
> Tony
